{"tid":1236231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭可以係中央既傀儡，都可以係人民既傀儡？","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T11:30:36.000Z","uid":35190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5020785939983a4a6e070e6c6acde769c2e414ed","tid":1236231,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"咩意思？<br />\n首先，反送中只係一個階段，唔係完結，而林鄭已經半跪。<br />\n一如陳伯所言。<br />\n既然我地有動員100-200萬人既力量，即係話，<br />\n我地想起多幾間公營醫院，可以用人數提出；<br />\n我地想提高最低公資，可以用人數提出；<br />\n甚至要求加強監警既權力等等。<br />\n當佢下下都出動速龍掃場時，<br />\n只怕係佢喊住想辭職。<br />\n（當然，斷佢米路既工作要持續進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"05fccdacc0702f45c4aa9b4d6860eafbb885aa92","tid":1236231,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:30:36.000Z","msg":"出面已經好多post講緊同一個問題。<br />\n我覺得黎緊既三罷可以先更明確focus我地既目標，<br />\n推到林鄭做埋警察眼中釘（欠缺任何威信的上司）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便比林鄭還下債先"}]}